modules.description: This module implements Snappy compression and decompression for strings, providing direct operations to compress data, validate compressed data, determine the size of uncompressed data, and decompress it. It supports both whole-string and substring-based processing, with safe and unsafe variants for performance-critical or controlled environments. Concrete use cases include efficiently compressing and decompressing data streams, verifying integrity of compressed payloads, and precomputing buffer sizes for network or storage operations.
